The application can be run by the typing make command in the directory.

1. The bunny can be rotated by clicking on the leftmouse button and choosing the direction.

2. The bunny can be moved by clicking on both right and left button of the mouse and choosing the direction.

3. The other things can be choosen by clicking on the right button of the mouse and choosing the operation intuitively.

4. The zoom can be done  by clicking on '+' and '-'  for zoom-in and zoom-out respectively.

5. The rotations with light can be done by clicking on the l button of the keyboard.


